physical_examinations.relevant_findings: Stocky body habitus, slightly overweight (95%), height appropriate for genetic height, mildly upslanting palpebral fissures, narrow and tortuous ear canals, beaked nose with anteverted nares, hypoplastic philtrum and a small mouth, high arched palate, small widely spaced teeth, short neck, low posterior hairline, mild dorsocervical fat pad, anisomastia, thin extremities with bilateral clinodactyly and contractures of the third, fourth, and fifth fingers, hyperextensibility of metacarpal joints, skin lentigines and fewer nevi.
